openAzFunctionIdToXacmlFunctionIdMap

public static final java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> openAzFunctionIdToXacmlFunctionIdMap
Table to map openaz "shorthand" strings for FunctionId<type> to the xacml "long" URI official FunctionId<type> names

Note: there is overlap with this table and the MatchId table. MatchIds can be considered the subset of FunctionIds that can be used in the Policy Match statements in Target elements, as opposed to the more broad set of FunctionIds that can be used in Condition statements.
